    "Subjective norms refer to individual expectations and pressures for others and the degree of attention paid to others evaluations.",
    "Perceived behavioral control is the degree of confidence that they can control their behavior (Ajzen, 1985 (Ajzen,, 1991;; Fishbein and Ajzen, 2011).",
    "According to the TPB, these three core concepts determine an individual's purchase intentions.",
